lass":68,"line":507},[66,664,589],{"class":72},[66,666,277],{"class":80},[66,668,168],{"class":72},[16,670,671],{},"所以目前顯示畫面是這樣 ↓",[16,673,674],{},[240,675],{"alt":676,"src":677},"目前顯示","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FCZKDsBc.png",[16,679,680,681,684,685,687,688,691],{},"正常來講當我們點擊任何一個 ",[30,682,683],{},"box1 ~ 2"," 都應該只會出現我們點擊的 box，但是如果我們將第三個參數改為 ",[30,686,277],{}," 並點擊 ",[30,689,690],{},"box2"," 將會發生什麼事情呢?",[16,693,694],{},[240,695],{"alt":696,"src":697},"box1 → box2","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F0tQVrSs.png",[16,699,700,701,703,704,707,708,710,711,713],{},"可以發現明明點擊的是 ",[30,702,690],{}," 但是 ",[30,705,706],{},"box1"," 卻也跳出來，那如果將第三個參數改為預設 ",[30,709,281],{}," 在點一次 ",[30,712,690],{}," 呢?",[16,715,716],{},[240,717],{"alt":718,"src":719},"box2 → box1","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FYBeUV9p.png",[16,721,722,723,725,726,728],{},"可以發現結果反過來輸出，而且還會穿透過去，所以說第三個參數的 ",[30,724,281],{}," & ",[30,727,277],{}," 分別代表著以下意思：",[730,731,732,738],"ul",{},[733,734,735,737],"li",{},[30,736,281],{}," - 從指定元素往外層觸發",[733,739,740,742],{},[30,741,277],{}," - 由外層往指定元素觸發",[16,744,745,746,748],{},"若是以圖片來範例的話就會像這樣，首先是預設的 ",[30,747,281],{}," 狀況 ↓",[16,750,751],{},[240,752],{"alt":753,"src":754},"從指定元素往外層觸發","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FHx6ZhOz.png",[16,756,757,758,760],{},"那麼 ",[30,759,277],{}," 則是反過來 ↓",[16,762,763],{},[240,764],{"alt":765,"src":766},"由外層往指定元素觸發","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FzB2q7bx.png",[16,768,769],{},"當然第三個參數是有比較正式的說法",[730,771,772,777],{},[733,773,774,776],{},[30,775,281],{}," - 事件氣泡(Event Bubbling)",[733,778,779,781],{},[30,780,277],{}," - 事件捕捉(Event capturing)",[16,783,784],{},"事件氣泡的意思，以異世界來舉例，你可以想像成你在大草原上面看著一個兔子(指定元素)，然後再往其他草原(外層)的部分尋找別的兔子。",[16,786,787],{},"那麼事件捕捉的話，則是你從大草原(外層)裡面尋找一隻兔子(指定元素)。",[16,789,790,791,794,795,797,798,236],{},"但是有時候我們會不希望發生事件氣泡 or 事件捕捉的狀況，那麼 JavaScript 就有提供一個語法幫助我們解決這個問題，也就是 ",[30,792,793],{},"stopPropagation();","，也就是阻止當前事件繼續進行捕捉（capturing）及冒泡（bubbling）階段的傳遞，當你加入後不管怎麼點 ",[30,796,690],{}," 就不會跳出 ",[30,799,706],{},[16,801,802],{},[240,803],{"alt":804,"src":805},"stopPropagation","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FdbB70hh.png",[16,807,103,808],{},[105,809,810],{"href":810,"rel":811},"https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fpen\u002FxxKYxro\u002F",[109],[111,813],{"default-tab":264,"height":114,"slug":814,"title":815,"user":117},"xxKYxro","事件氣泡",[12,817,818],{"id":818},"結尾",[16,820,821],{},"下一篇的 RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活-第五日 將會介紹陣列與物件。",[823,824,825],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}",{"title":62,"searchDepth":144,"depth":144,"links":827},[828,829,830,831,832],{"id":14,"depth":144,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":144,"text":22},{"id":120,"depth":144,"text":120},{"id":268,"depth":144,"text":268},{"id":818,"depth":144,"text":818},"JavaScript","2019-09-19 00:01:10","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fre-js\u002Fep-4-re-js","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活\u002FEP-4-RE：從零開始的學習-JS-生活-第四日",[833,844,845],"RE：從零開始的學習 JS 生活","第 11 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fjavascrip